headline: Pressure grows on Target as activist investor builds stake
summary: US retail chain Target is facing pressure from an activist investor after a sales slump that has wiped out nearly a third of its share value...

headline: Target shares gain as activist investor reportedly builds big stake
summary: Investing.com -- Target shares are gaining roughly 3.3% in early trading on Friday after the Financial Times reported that activist investor Toms Capital Investment Management has acquired a significant stake in the retail chain.
